Hvala vam, gospodine.

69
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:37,280
Hvala vam, gospodine.

70
00:23:37,440 --> 00:23:38,400
Hvala vam, gospodine.

71
00:23:39,760 --> 00:23:44,160
